Package org.peertrust.tnviz.app

Interface Summary
Graphics The interface for the Graphics classes.
 

Class Summary
TNEdge The TNEdge class is a custom version of the DefaultEdge class.
TNGraphics The TNGraphics class implements the Graphics interface and is responsible for mainatining the different diagramms and for forwarding changing to them.
TNNode The TNNode class is a custom version of the DefaultGraphCell class.
TNReplay The TNReplay class provides the means to visualize the sequence in which a graph was built.
TNSeqDiagramm The TNSeqDiagramm class provides the means to create and maintain a sequence diagramm.
TNTreeDiagramm * The TNTreeDiagramm class provides the means to create and maintain a * tree diagramm.
TNVizListener The TNVizListener class can be used by PeerTrust in order to create and maintain the diagramms.
